.SH Description
.PP
\f[C]djpi2\f[R] will calculate the rotation matrix
\f[C]d_{mM}\[ha]j (pi/2)\f[R] that is used in rotating spherical
harmonics in the routines \f[C]SHRotateRealCoef\f[R] and
\f[C]SHRotateCoef\f[R].
